  "texts": [
    "This approach first transforms textual content into graph structures and uses stacked graph pooling networks to deeply mine the hierarchical semantic interactions between questions and answers.",
    "Meanwhile, the introduced convolutional matching network is able to synthesize these hierarchical semantic features and accurately infer the matching scores.",
    "This innovation not only improves the accuracy of question-answer matching, but also enhances the interpretability and generalization ability of the system.",
    "In the field of Natural Language Processing (NLP), graph pooling methods are gradually highlighting their incomparable value.",
    "In advancing the development of multimodal Community Question and Answer (CQA) systems, (Hu et al. 2019) successfully extracted key information by carefully constructing a multimodal Q&A graph and combining it with a hierarchical graph semantic pooling operation, thus significantly improving the accuracy of question-answer matching."
